        boolean isNewerThan(int lastLogIndex,
                    int lastLogTerm)
        Return if the candidate's last log entry is newer than the leader's last log entry.
        参数:
        lastLogIndex - the index of the leader's last log entry
        lastLogTerm - the term of the leader's last log entry
        返回:
        true if the candidate's last log entry is newer than the leader's last log, otherwise false

      • appendEntriesFromLeader

        boolean appendEntriesFromLeader(int prevLogIndex,
                                int prevLogTerm,
                                List<Entry> leaderEntries)
        Append log entries to log.
        参数:
        prevLogIndex - expected index of previous log entry
        prevLogTerm - expected term of previous log entry
        leaderEntries - log entries from leader to be appended
        返回:
        true if succeeded, false if previous log check failed

      • advanceCommitIndex

        void advanceCommitIndex(int newCommitIndex,
                        int currentTerm)
        Advance commitIndex.

        The log entry with new commitIndex must be the same term sa the one in parameter, otherwise commit index will not change.

        参数:
        newCommitIndex - new commitIndex
        currentTerm - current term
